    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "professionals wouldnt fix the debt, they just charge more money. i look at them and i just think... what if i wasn't here? what if they didn't have to worry about me being another mouth to feed or another problem to solve? it almost sounds better, doesn't it? just being gone so they can start over without all this weight.",
